OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775823082
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FPassengers without EU passports will
OL,7,Fbe required to have their fingerprints
OL,8,Fand photographs taken, as Senior
OL,9,FCorrespondent Jonathan Swain reports
OL,11,FA new Entry/Exit system will be fully
OL,12,Fimplemented across all EU airports and
OL,13,Fports from Friday, meaning British
OL,14,Ftravellers will no longer need to have
OL,15,Ftheir passports stamped.
OL,17,FPhysical stamps from passport officers
OL,18,Fare being phased out, in place of a
OL,19,Fdigital biometric system, in a bid to
OL,20,Fmake entering the EU from non-Schengen
OL,21,Farea countries quicker.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
