OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775823082
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FIt has been introduced to strengthen
OL,7,Fborder security, detect overstays and
OL,8,Fis supposed to improve processing
OL,9,Fspeeds at airports.
OL,11,FHowever, concerns remain that the new
OL,12,Fsystem could bring delays, however, as
OL,13,Fairports adjust to the new system.
OL,15,FUntil now many airports were
OL,16,Feffectively running a double system,
OL,17,Fwith both passport stamps being taken
OL,18,Fand the new biometric digital EES
OL,19,F(Entry/Exit system) also being carried
OL,20,Fout.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775823082
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FThis double-entry recording has led to
OL,7,Fnumerous delays at airports across the
OL,8,Fbloc, with Brits complaining of multi-
OL,9,Fhour waits to get through airports,
OL,10,Fand there are concerns that the
OL,11,Fchanges could cause further delays for
OL,12,Ftravellers.
OL,14,FITV News explains how the new system
OL,15,Fwill work.
OL,17,FWhat is the Entry/Exit system?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775823082
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FNon-EU nationals wishing to enter the
OL,7,FSchengen area will now go through
OL,8,Fbiometric checks instead of getting a
OL,9,Fpassport stamp when entering the area.
OL,11,FThese checks will involve face scans
OL,12,Fand fingerprint recording. Children
OL,13,Funder the age of 12 will not need to
OL,14,Fhave their fingerprints scanned.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775823082
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FTravellers will also go through the
OL,7,Fsame check when leaving the area,
OL,8,Fmeaning country's can track when
OL,9,Fvisitors overstay.
OL,11,FOnce registered, subsequent entries to
OL,12,Fthe bloc will be quicker, as the
OL,13,Fbiometrics will only need to be
OL,14,Fscanned rather than registered. The
OL,15,Fdigital record will be valid for three
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,FTravellers will not need to take any
OL,19,Faction before their journey.
OL,21,FWho will be affected?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
