OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775823082
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FThe changes will mostly affect people
OL,7,Ffrom non-EU countries, including those
OL,8,Ffrom the UK.
OL,10,FIt affects all countries in the
OL,11,FSchengen area, which includes France,
OL,12,FSpain and Germany. Ireland is not
OL,13,Fwithin this area and travel there is
OL,14,Fnot be impacted by the new rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
