PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775823082
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FIt should only take a few minutes, but
OL,7,Fthere have been reports of significant
OL,8,Fdelays as airports struggle with the
OL,9,Fnew system.
OL,11,FThere is a small list of other
OL,12,Fexceptions for UK nationals, which can
OL,13,Fbe found on the EES website.
OL,15,FWhy has the EU introduced the new
OL,16,Fsystem?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1775823082
OL,3,CNew EU entry system in force: How does
OL,4,Cit work and could you be delayed?
OL,6,FThe EES is designed to give border
OL,7,Fauthorities a more accurate record of
OL,8,Fwho enters and leaves the Schengen
OL,9,Farea, and to automatically spot people
OL,10,Fwho overstay their visas.
OL,12,FThe EU also says the system should
OL,13,Fhelp tackle document and identity
OL,14,Ffraud, strengthen security by giving
OL,15,Fauthorities more reliable real-time
OL,16,Finformation, and make border checks
OL,17,Fmore efficient through greater use of
OL,18,Fautomated controls and self-service
OL,19,Fsystems.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
